Package: pedvis
Type: Package
Title: Simple drawing of pedigrees with dot
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2014-05-18
Author: Eric C. Anderson
Maintainer: Who to complain to <eric.anderson@noaa.gov>
Description: Given a pedigree specification in a data frame this will write a
    .dot file and run dot on it.  Will make marriage node diagrams and modified
    factor graphs.
License: Public Domain.  See TERMS.md
